  <brief_title>Effects of Endurance Training on Patients With Reduced Left Ventricular Ejection Fraction (LVEF) and Cardiac Resynchronisation Therapy Especially for Cardiac Arrhythmias</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Endurance Training on Patients With Reduced LVEF and Cardiac Resynchronisation Therapy Especially for Cardiac Arrhythmias</official_title>
